text: Love the atmosphere! So peaceful alfresco on a Saturday evening

A great place to go for if u want to chill relax beer and satay 'alfresco' with indoor sitting option plus car park at along road side. Good satay and Thai food. Support this place as such place is getting lesser in SG without burning pockets.
Great spot for a casual dinner or drinks with friends!

Relaxing and chill atmosphere to hang out and chill out with friends and family over some good food and drinks.

Place is clean, airy and well lit.
Free parking within its coffeeshop premises and daily after 5pm.
One of the best chill out place~
